TY  - JOUR
T1  - On the Optimality of Pure Strategies
AU  - Wagner, Harvey M.
Y1  - 1960/04/01
PY  - 1960
DA  - 1960/04/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.6.3.268
DO  - 10.1287/mnsc.6.3.268
T2  - Management Science
JF  - Management Science
JO  - Management Science
SP  - 268
EP  - 269
VL  - 6
IS  - 3
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - In Manne [Manne, A. S. 1960. Linear programming and sequential decisions. Management Sci. (April).] has suggested a linear programming formulation for on optimal steady state solution of sequential decision models. In this note we offer a proof which appeals primarily to the properties of linear programs that an optimal solution exists involving only pure strategies.
